          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-1" n="1">I.<lb/><hi rend="display-initial">F</hi>Lutt'ring spread thy purple pinions,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-2" n="2">Gentle Cupid, o'er my heart;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-3" n="3">I a slave in thy dominions;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-4" n="4">Nature must give way to art.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-5" n="5">II.<lb/>Mild Arcadians, ever blooming,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-6" n="6">Nightly nodding o'er your flocks,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-7" n="7">See my weary days consuming</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-8" n="8">All beneath yon flow'ry rocks.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-9" n="9">III.<lb/>Thus the Cyprian goddess weeping</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-10" n="10">Mourn'd Adonis, darling youth:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-11" n="11">Him the boar in silence creeping,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-12" n="12">Gor'd with unrelenting tooth.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-13" n="13">IV.<lb/>Cynthia, tune harmonious numbers;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-14" n="14">Fair <hi rend="italics">Discretion</hi>, string the lyre;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-15" n="15">Sooth my ever-waking slumbers:</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-16" n="16">Bright Apollo, lend thy choir.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-17" n="17">V.<lb/>Gloomy Pluto, king of terrors,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-18" n="18">Arm'd in adamantine chains,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-19" n="19">Lead me to the crystal mirrors,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-20" n="20">Wat'ring soft Elysian plains.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-21" n="21">VI.<lb/>Mournful cypress, verdant willow,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-22" n="22">Gilding my Aurelia's brows,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-23" n="23">Morpheus hov'ring o'er my pillow,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-24" n="24">Hear me pay my dying vows.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-25" n="25">VII.<lb/>Melancholy smooth Meander</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-26" n="26">Swiftly purling in a round,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-27" n="27">On thy margin lovers wander,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-28" n="28">With thy flow'ry chaplets crown'd,</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-29" n="29">VIII.<lb/>Thus when Philomela drooping</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-30" n="30">Softly seeks her silent mate,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-31" n="31">See the bird of Juno stooping;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-660-07G1-line-32" n="32">Melody resigns to fate.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
